 everyone deserves wholesome, delicious food. That\'s why our founder, Lucinda, tested hundreds of recipes until she finally found the one that made her friends and family say \"mmm.\" Genius is baked fresh with naturally gluten free whole grains and seeds. Enjoy it just like the bread you remember - fresh or toasted, served at every meal and occasion.</p>'),(5432,247,'_blocks_7_content','field_58b99c3386a14'),(5433,247,'blocks_7_width','container'),(5434,247,'_blocks_7_width','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a114a1e6b'),(5435,247,'blocks_7_height','auto'),(5436,247,'_blocks_7_height','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a13ca1e6c'),(5437,247,'blocks_7_enable_background_overlay','0'),(5438,247,'_blocks_7_enable_background_overlay','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a084a1e67'),(5439,247,'blocks_7_background_image',''),(5440,247,'_blocks_7_background_image','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a0a5a1e68'),(5441,247,'blocks_7_select_brand_color','white'),(5442,247,'_blocks_7_select_brand_color','field_58b9a29159eba_field_5967cba998df0'),(5443,247,'blocks_7_background_style','cover'),(5444,247,'_blocks_7_background_style','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58e28ee4f5088'),(5445,247,'blocks_7_repeat_background','0'),(5446,247,'_blocks_7_repeat_background','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58e28f12f508a'),(5447,247,'blocks_7_padding','0'),(5448,247,'_blocks_7_padding','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a0f9a1e6a'),(5449,247,'blocks_7_additional_classes',''),(5450,247,'_blocks_7_additional_classes','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a15aa1e6d'),(5451,247,'blocks_7_custom_id',''),(5452,247,'_blocks_7_custom_id','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a16fa1e6e'),(5453,247,'blocks_7_disable_block','0'),(5454,247,'_blocks_7_disable_block','field_58b9a29159eba_field_5903740fa0718'),(5455,247,'blocks_7_administrative_name',''),(5456,247,'_blocks_7_administrative_name','field_58b9a29159eba_field_591340bb5f01a'),(5457,247,'blocks_6_photo','241'),(5458,247,'_blocks_6_photo','field_58b99c4286a15'),(5459,247,'blocks_6_content','<h