	<li>Heat oil or butter in a frying pan, then fry the bread a few slices at a time until golden brown. Place in the oven to keep warm.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dredge the warm French toast with the cinnamon powdered sugar mix. Stack three pieces of French toast on warmed plates. Serve immediately.</li>\r\n</ol>'),(6590,254,'_directions','field_59678c403d346'),(6591,254,'ingredients_0_ingredient','2 medium eggs, beaten'),(6592,254,'_ingredients_0_ingredient','field_59678c533d348'),(6593,254,'ingredients_1_ingredient','5 ounces milk or dairy-free milk'),(6594,254,'_ingredients_1_ingredient','field_59678c533d348'),(6595,254,'ingredients_2_ingredient','1 tablespoon runny honey'),(6596,254,'_ingredients_2_ingredient','field_59678c533d348'),(6597,254,'ingredients_3_ingredient','1/2 teaspoon cinnamon'),(6598,254,'_ingredients_3_ingredient','field_59678c533d348'),(6599,254,'ingredients_4_ingredient','6 slices Genius Gluten Free white, cinnamon raisin or brown bread, sliced in half diagonally'),(6600,254,'_ingredients_4_ingredient','field_59678c533d348'),(6601,254,'ingredients_5_ingredient','2 tablespoons oil or butter for shallow frying'),(6602,254,'_ingredients_5_ingredient','field_59678c533d348'),(6603,254,'ingredients_6_ingredient','1 tablespoon powdered sugar mixed with 1 teaspoon ground cinnamon'),(6604,254,'_ingredients_6_ingredient','field_59678c533d348'),(6605,254,'ingredients_7_ingredient','Summer berries or bananas and honey for topping'),(6606,254,'_ingredients_7_ingredient','field_59678c533d348'),(6607,254,'ingredients','8'),(6608,254,'_ingredients','field_59678c4c3d347'),(6609,2,'blocks_8_recipes','a:4:{i:0;s:3:\"254\";i:1;s:3:\"262\";i:2;s:3:\"264\";i:3;s:3:\"266\";}'),(6610,2,'_blocks_8_recipes','field_596cd2c258588'),(6611,2,'blocks_8_width','container'),(6612,2,'_blocks_8_width','field_596cd2a158587_field_58b9a114a1e6b'),(6613,2,'blocks_8_height','auto'),(6614,2,'_blocks_8_height','field_596cd2a158587_field_58b9a13ca1e6c'),(6615,2,'blocks_8_enable_background_overlay',