read ready for them to try. Somewhere along the line, Lucinda even broke her oven, but in 2009 Genius gluten free bread hit the shelves.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n'),(7172,268,'_blocks_5_content','field_57b66234b32d6'),(7173,268,'blocks_5_cta_arrow','0'),(7174,268,'_blocks_5_cta_arrow','field_59245a3bddfed'),(7175,268,'blocks_5_width','container'),(7176,268,'_blocks_5_width','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a114a1e6b'),(7177,268,'blocks_5_height','auto'),(7178,268,'_blocks_5_height','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a13ca1e6c'),(7179,268,'blocks_5_enable_background_overlay','0'),(7180,268,'_blocks_5_enable_background_overlay','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a084a1e67'),(7181,268,'blocks_5_background_image',''),(7182,268,'_blocks_5_background_image','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a0a5a1e68'),(7183,268,'blocks_5_select_brand_color','accent'),(7184,268,'_blocks_5_select_brand_color','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_5967cba998df0'),(7185,268,'blocks_5_background_style','cover'),(7186,268,'_blocks_5_background_style','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58e28ee4f5088'),(7187,268,'blocks_5_repeat_background','0'),(7188,268,'_blocks_5_repeat_background','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58e28f12f508a'),(7189,268,'blocks_5_padding','0'),(7190,268,'_blocks_5_padding','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a0f9a1e6a'),(7191,268,'blocks_5_additional_classes',''),(7192,268,'_blocks_5_additional_classes','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a15aa1e6d'),(7193,268,'blocks_5_custom_id',''),(7194,268,'_blocks_5_custom_id','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a16fa1e6e'),(7195,268,'blocks_5_disable_block','0'),(7196,268,'_blocks_5_disable_block','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_5903740fa0718'),(7197,268,'blocks_5_administrative_name',''),(7198,268,'_blocks_5_administrative_name','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_591340bb5f01a'),(7199,268,'blocks_7_photo','244'),(7200,268,'_blocks_7_photo','field_58b99c4286a15'),(7201,268,'blocks_7_content','<h2>Our Purpose</h2>\r\n<p class=\"headline--description text--grey\">We believe that everyone deserves wholesome, delicious food. That\'s why our founder, Lucinda, tested hundreds of recipes until she finally found the one that made her friends and family say \"mmm.\" Genius is baked fresh with naturally gluten free whole grains and seeds. Enjoy it just like the bread you remember - fresh or toasted, served at every meal and occasion.</p>'),(7202,268,'_blocks_7_content','field_58b99c3386a14'),(7203,268,'blocks_7_width','container'),(7204,268,'_blocks_7_width','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a114a1e6b'),(7205,268,'blocks_7_height','auto'),(7206,268,'_blocks_7_height','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a13ca1e6c'),(7207,268,'blocks_7_enable_background_overlay','0'),(7208,268,'_blocks_7_enable_background_overlay','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a084a1e67'),(7209,268,'blocks_7_background_image',''),(7210,268,'_blocks_7_background_image','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a0a5a1e68'),(7211,268,'blocks_7_select_brand_color','white'),(7212,268,'_blocks_7_select_brand_color','field_58b9a29159eba_field_5967cba998df0'),(7213,268,'blocks_7_background_style','cover'),(7214,268,'_blocks_7_background_style','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58e28ee4f5088'),(7215,268,'blocks_7_repeat_background','0'),(7216,268,'_blocks_7_repeat_background','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58e28f12f508a'),(7217,268,'blocks_7_padding','0'),(7218,268,'_blocks_7_padding','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a0f9a1e6a'),(7219,268,'blocks_7_additional_classes',''),(7220,268,'_blocks_7_additional_classes','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a15aa1e6d'),(7221,268,'blocks_7_custom_id',''),(7222,268,'_blocks_7_custom_id','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a16fa1e6e'),(7223,268,'blocks_7_disable_block','0'),(7224,268,'_blocks_7_disable_block','field_58b9a29159eba_field_5903740fa0718'),(7225,268,'blocks_7_administrative_name',''),(7226,268,'_blocks_7_administrative_name','field_58b9a29159eba_field_591340bb5f01a'),(7227,268,'blocks_6_photo','241'),(7228,268,'_blocks_6_photo','field_58b99c4286a15'),(7229,268,'blocks_6_content','<h2>What is Gluten Free?</h2>\r\n<p class=\"headline--description text--grey\">Gluten is a protein found in wheat, barley and rye. It’s what gives pizza dough its stretchy elasticity and makes bread and cookies rise in the oven. Cooking without gluten requires creativity and determination, which is why Genius is proud to be  gluten free.</p>'),(7230,268,'_blocks_6_content','field_58b99c3386a14'),(7231,268,'blocks_6_width','container'),(7232,268,'_blocks_6_width','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a114a1e6b'),(7233,268,'blocks_6_height','auto'),(7234,268,'_blocks_6_height','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a13ca1e6c'),(7235,268,'blocks_6_enable_background_overlay','0'),(7236,268,'_blocks_6_enable_background_overlay','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a084a1e67'),(7237,268,'blocks_6_background_image',''),(7238,268,'_blocks_6_background_image','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a0a5a1e68'),(7239,268,'blocks_6_select_brand_color','white'),(7240,268,'_blocks_6_select_brand_color','field_58b9a29159eba_field_5967cba998df0'),(7241,268,'blocks_6_background_style','cover'),(7242,268,'_blocks_6_background_style','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58e28ee4f5088'),(7243,268,'blocks_6_repeat_background','0'),(7244,268,'_blocks_6_repeat_background','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58e28f12f508a'),(7245,268,'blocks_6_padding','0'),(7246,268,'_blocks_6_padding','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a0f9a1e6a'),(7247,268,'blocks_6_additional_classes',''),(7248,268,'_blocks_6_additional_classes','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a15aa1e6d'),(7249,268,'blocks_6_custom_id',''),(7250,268,'_blocks_6_custom_id','field_58b9a29159eba_field_58b9a16fa1e6e'),(7251,268,'blocks_6_disable_block','0'),(7252,268,'_blocks_6_disable_block','field_58b9a29159eba_field_5903740fa0718'),(7253,268,'blocks_6_administrative_name',''),(7254,268,'_blocks_6_administrative_name','field_58b9a29159eba_field_591340bb5f01a'),(7255,268,'blocks_8_recipes','a:4:{i:0;s:3:\"254\";i:1;s:3:\"262\";i:2;s:3:\"264\";i:3;s:3:\"266\";}'),(7256,268,'_blocks_8_recipes','field_596cd2c25