 gluten free bread. She knew she had a big idea when she couldn’t find an alternative anywhere to the brick-like, vacuum-packed offerings on supermarket shelves.</p>\r\n        <p class=\"text--white\">It wasn’t unusual for Lucinda’s kids to arrive home from school with 14 different loaves of bread ready for them to try. Somewhere along the line, Lucinda even broke her oven, but in 2009 Genius gluten free bread hit the shelves.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n'),(7760,270,'_blocks_5_content','field_57b66234b32d6'),(7761,270,'blocks_5_cta_arrow','0'),(7762,270,'_blocks_5_cta_arrow','field_59245a3bddfed'),(7763,270,'blocks_5_width','container'),(7764,270,'_blocks_5_width','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a114a1e6b'),(7765,270,'blocks_5_height','auto'),(7766,270,'_blocks_5_height','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a13ca1e6c'),(7767,270,'blocks_5_enable_background_overlay','0'),(7768,270,'_blocks_5_enable_background_overlay','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a084a1e67'),(7769,270,'blocks_5_background_image',''),(7770,270,'_blocks_5_background_image','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a0a5a1e68'),(7771,270,'blocks_5_select_brand_color','accent'),(7772,270,'_blocks_5_select_brand_color','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_5967cba998df0'),(7773,270,'blocks_5_background_style','cover'),(7774,270,'_blocks_5_background_style','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58e28ee4f5088'),(7775,270,'blocks_5_repeat_background','0'),(7776,270,'_blocks_5_repeat_background','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58e28f12f508a'),(7777,270,'blocks_5_padding','0'),(7778,270,'_blocks_5_padding','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a0f9a1e6a'),(7779,270,'blocks_5_additional_classes',''),(7780,270,'_blocks_5_additional_classes','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a15aa1e6d'),(7781,270,'blocks_5_custom_id',''),(7782,270,'_blocks_5_custom_id','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a16fa1e6e'),(7783,270,'blocks_5_disable_block','0'),(7784,270,'_blocks_5_disable_block','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_5903740fa0718'),(7785,270,'blocks_5_administrative_name',''),(7786