hEfs?ecver=1\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n        <h3>Softness</h3>\r\n        <p class=\"headline--description text--primary-light\">Soft enough for sandwiches, sturdy enough for toppings.<p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"medium-4 columns push-down--double-small\">\r\n        <iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"210\" class=\"push-down--double\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/GArwAXhCfgE?ecver=1\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n        <h3>Aroma</h3>\r\n        <p class=\"headline--description text--primary-light\">Smells like bread should &ndash; warm and homey, just like mom\'s kitchen.<p>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>'),(11990,333,'_blocks_3_content','field_57b66234b32d6'),(11991,333,'blocks_3_cta_arrow','0'),(11992,333,'_blocks_3_cta_arrow','field_59245a3bddfed'),(11993,333,'blocks_3_width','container'),(11994,333,'_blocks_3_width','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a114a1e6b'),(11995,333,'blocks_3_height','auto'),(11996,333,'_blocks_3_height','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a13ca1e6c'),(11997,333,'blocks_3_enable_background_overlay','0'),(11998,333,'_blocks_3_enable_background_overlay','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a084a1e67'),(11999,333,'blocks_3_background_image',''),(12000,333,'_blocks_3_background_image','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a0a5a1e68'),(12001,333,'blocks_3_select_brand_color','accent-light'),(12002,333,'_blocks_3_select_brand_color','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_5967cba998df0'),(12003,333,'blocks_3_background_style','cover'),(12004,333,'_blocks_3_background_style','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58e28ee4f5088'),(12005,333,'blocks_3_repeat_background','0'),(12006,333,'_blocks_3_repeat_background','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58e28f12f508a'),(12007,333,'blocks_3_padding','0'),(12008,333,'_blocks_3_padding','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a0f9a1e6a'),(12009,333,'blocks_3_additional_classes',''),(12010,333,'_blocks_3_additional_classes','field_58b9a2429eb95_field_58b9a15aa1e6d'),(12011,333,'blocks_3_custom_id',''),(12012,333,'_blo